div.p: This architecture ingests live flight data through an external API, which acts as a data producer for PostgreSQL. Debezium captures change events from PostgreSQL and streams them to Kafka. Kafka feeds Snowpipe Streaming, which loads the data into Snowflake in real time. GitHub Actions automates deployment and executes updated PostgreSQL and Snowflake scripts across services. Datadog and Power BI enable monitoring, logging, and data consistency validation.
